Olive Fremstad https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Olive_Fremstad 0 Olive Fremstad (14 March 1871 – 21 April 1951) was the stage name of Anna Olivia Rundquist, a celebrated Swedish-American opera diva who sang in both the mezzo-soprano and soprano ranges.
